import { useState } from "react"; function EditContact({ contact }) { const [firstName, setFirstName] = useState(contact.firstName); const [lastName, setLastName] = useState(contact.lastName); const [email, setEmail] = useState(contact.email); const [phoneNumber, setPhoneNumber] = useState(contact.phoneNumber); const [houseYard, setHouseYard] = useState(contact.houseYard); const [suite, setSuite] = useState(contact.suite); const [classYear, setClassYear] = useState(contact.classYear); const [homeCity, setHomeCity] = useState(contact.homeCity); const [homeState, setHomeState] = useState(contact.homeState); const [contactStatus, setContactStatus] = useState(contact.contactStatus); const [pteStatus, setPTEStatus] = useState(contact.pteStatus); const [registrationStatus, setRegistrationStatus] = useState(contact.registrationStatus); const [stageOfVotingProcess, setStageOfVotingProcess] = useState(contact.stageOfVotingProcess); const [whereRegistered, setWhereRegistered] = useState(contact.whereRegistered); return (
); } export default EditContact;
